melodic roles are handled.\n- 2733 tests pass across the entire suite, confirming no regressions.\n\n## Issues Found\n- None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nImplementation is solid. The use of metadata for silence budget accounting is appropriate given that R10 is a separate, future task.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-008@20260416t181925z-verify.md"}}
